@startuml tea-machine
Start: initialize
Start -> Idle
Idle: Waiting for input
Idle -> Interface: Select product
Interface: Ask for money
Interface --> Interface: Not enough money
Interface --> MakeDrink: Enough money
MakeDrink -> DoneDrink: Poured and waited
MakeDrink -> MakeDrink: Still making
DoneDrink -> Idle: Reset
@enduml
